)<br>6. DNA Storage (DNA \uc800\uc7a5\uc18c)}}\n|rowspan=2|Kang Ho-dong\n|\n|-\n!rowspan=2|'''6'''\n|rowspan=2|5 August 2018\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||7. Zone E (E\uad6c\uc5ed)<br>8. Zone C (C\uad6c\uc5ed)<br>'''{{big|Escape successfully!!!}}''' (with the story character).}}\n|{{small|Special appearance: [[:ko:\uc591\ubc30\ucc28|Yang Bae-cha]]}}\n|-\n|rowspan=3|4\n|rowspan=3|Evil Prison (\uc545\ub839\uac10\uc625)<br>{{small|(Villa of Shaman \ucc9c\ud574\uba85)}}\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||'''1. Third Floor (3\uce35)'''<br>''{{small|1.1 Third Floor Attic Room 1 (3\uce35 \ub2e4\ub77d1\ubc29)<br>1.2 Third Floor Attic Room 2 (3\uce35 \ub2e4\ub77d2\ubc29)}}''}}\n|rowspan=3|Kim Dong-hyun\n|rowspan=3|\n|-\n!'''7'''\n|12 August 2018\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||'''1. Third Floor (3\uce35)'''<br>''{{small|1.3 Third Floor Living Room (3\uce35 \uac70\uc2e4)<br>1.4 Attic Warehouse (\ub2e4\ub77d \ucc3d\uace0)<br>1.5 Water Tank (\ubb3c\ud0f1\ud06c)<br>1.6 Music Appreciation Room (\ub9c9\ubc14\uc9c0 \uc5ec\ub984\ud734\uac00)}}''<br>'''2. Second Floor (2\uce35)'''<br>''{{small|2.1 Second Floor Living Room (2\uce35 \uac70\uc2e4)<br>2.2 Kitchen (\uc8fc\ubc29)<br>2.3 Urn Room (\ubd84\uace8\ud568\ubc29)<br>2.4 Doll's Room (\uc778\ud615\uc758\ubc29)<br>2.5 Shaman's Room (\ubb34\ub2f9\uc758\ubc29)<br>2.6 Wardrobe (\uc758\uc0c1\uc2e4)}}''}}\n|-\n!'''8'''\n|19 August 2018\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||'''2. Second Floor (2\uce35)'''<br>''{{small|2.7 Secret Room (\ube44\ubc00\uc758 \ubc29)<br>\u21922.7.1 Re-explore Music Appreciation Room (\ub9c9\ubc14\uc9c0 \uc5ec\ub984\ud734\uac00)}}'' on the Third Floor<br>''{{small|2.8 Corridor of second floor.<br>2.9 Re-explore Shaman's Room (\ubb34\ub2f9\uc758\ubc29)<br>\u21922.9.1 Shaman's Secret Room (\ubb34\ub2f9\uc758 \ube44\ubc00\uc758 \ubc29)<br>2.10 Re-explore Kitchen (\uc8fc\ubc29)}}''<br>'''3. First Floor (1\uce35)'''<br>''{{small|3.1 First Floor Kitchen (1\uce35 \uc8fc\ubc29)<br>3.2 First Floor Living Room (1\uce35 \uac70\uc2e4)<br>3.3 Cellar (\uc9c0\ud558\uc2e4)<br>3.4 Huge door (\uac70\ub300\ud55c \ubb38)}}''<br>'''{{big|Escape successfully!!!}}''' and helped the story characters by removing the large talismans.}}\n|-\n!'''9'''\n|rowspan=2|5\n|26 August 2018\n|rowspan=2|Bunker<br>(\ubc99\ucee4)\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||'''1. Living Space (\uac70\uc8fc\uacf5\uac04)'''<br>Found story character Jang Dong-min and clues tattooed on his body.<br>'''2. Theatre (\uadf9\uc7a5)'''<br>Watch 4 short movies and received clues FIVE-EIGHT-TWENTY to open link door of a tunnel.<br>'''3. Garden Field (\ud143\ubc2d)''' <br>Open Gate 1 with password (ANGEL \u2192 1004 (\ucc9c\uc0ac) in Hangul) found in Garden Field.<br>'''4. Grocery Store (\uc2dd\ub8cc\ud488 \ucc3d\uace0)'''<br>'''5. Treatment Room (\uce58\ub8cc\uc2e4)'''}}\n|rowspan=2|Kang Ho-dong\n|rowspan=2|{{small|Special appearance: [[Jang Dong-min]]}}<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2018082623110095435|title='\ub300\ud0c8\ucd9c' \uae40\ub3d9\ud604, \uae30\uc5b5\uc783\uc740 \uc7a5\ub3d9\ubbfc\uc5d0 \"\ub098\ub294 \uc7a5\ub3d9\uac74\"|website=mt.co.kr|accessdate=26 August 2018|date=26 August 2018|lang=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719084705/http://star.mt.co.kr/stview.php?no=2018082623110095435|archivedate=19 July 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n!'''10'''\n|{{date|2 Sep 2018}}\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||'''5. Treatment Room (\uce58\ub8cc\uc2e4)''' <br>Found the password (2-5-3-8) under the cloth of the jig-saw puzzle and open Gate 2.<br>'''6. Arcade Room (\uc624\ub77d\uc2e4)''' <br>Jang Dong-min scored greater than 60 points on the basketball and receive 2nd part of password (0).<br>Kim Dong-hyun scored greater 850 on the King of Hammer and receive 3rd part of the password (0).<br>Kim Dong-hyun scored greater 850 on the Right Hook Power machine and receive 1st part of password (8).<br>All members failed to score greater 650 on the soccer ball machine to receive 4th part of password.<br>Found the password (5-0-7-8) on the arcade machine to open the Mother Room.<br>'''7. Mother Room (\uc5b4\uba38\ub2c8 \ubc29)''' <br>Yoo Byung-jae searched the enlarged map in the room and found password (7-0-7-1) for Gate 3 and passwords for the previous 2 gates.<br>'''8. Security room (\ubcf4\uc548\uc2e4)''' <br>Teamwork by the members to solve the arithmetic questions. Use the partial password from the Arcade Room (8-3-0-2) to open the safe.<br>Found a clue in the safe and password (6-3-5-2) by placing on the map on the back of Jang Dong-min to open the door of FINAL GATE.<br>'''{{big|Escape successfully!!!}}''' (with the story character).}}\n|-\n!'''11'''\n|rowspan=2|6\n|{{date|9 Sep 2018}}\n|rowspan=2|Tae-yang High School<br>(\ud0dc\uc591 \uc5ec\uace0)\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||'''1. Classroom 2-1 (\uad50\uc2e4 2-1)'''\n*Members are being placed into a classroom setting and to take a world history test with a class of high school girls. The history teacher announced that all students and members are able to go home if they can answer the questions without errors.\n*Two of the students were passing paper notes (intercepted by the members) to meet up at the Infirmary Room after the test and the physical education teacher will help them.\n*Members are punished for not answering correctly for the world history test and are told by the history teacher to stay in the punishment position till the end of the period.\n*The two students (Kim Mi-ra and Gu Ha-li) were caught passing paper notes by the history teacher and were ask to go to the Consultation Room.\n*The history teacher dismissed the students and left for the Consultation Room. The members started searching the Heo Sa-ra's locker and found a photo with 3 girls (Kim Mi-ra, Heo Sa-ra and Gu Ha-li). Ho-dong found a message at the back of the photo stating that Sa-ra is missing and both Mi-ra and Ha-li are all out to find the reason.\n*Members deduction about this challenge is to find the whereabouts of Heo Sa-ra.\n*The test paper left by Mi-ra has a drawing of something being ripped open.\n*Jong-min found on the class register that Sa-ra has withdraw from school as she did not attend classes for 20 times without valid reasons. 5 other students were transferred.\n*At the end of the period, the history teacher left the Consultant Room and locked the gate of the corridor to go to the second floor. Members have to find ways to open the gate.\n*Ho-dong forcefully broke the lock of Mi-ra locker but found no clues in it.\n*Shin-dong found out from the class register that the History Teacher's name is Ge Su-sang\n'''2. Consultation Room (\uc0c1\ub2f4\uc2e4)'''\n*The members enter the room any found no one in the room as they thought Mi-ra and Ho-li are in the room. They searched the room for more clues and found the paper, that Mi-ra and Ha-li were passing around, in the waste paper bin. This showed that the History teacher was in the room. \n*P.O found the 3 consultation files of Kim Mi-ra, Heo Sa-ra and Gu Ha-li. Byung-jae started to investigate the records in the 3 consultation files and observed that all 3 girls has some family issues.\n*Dong-hyun observed 2 bottles of empty \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" on the table and deduce that Mi-ra and Ha-li did enter the room.\n*Shin-dong found a clue from the paper shredder and the members start piecing the shredded clues. The clue is \"Do not read\". The staff prank the members and \"bombard\" the members with white flour when all the members read the \"clue\".\n'''3. Infirmary Room (\uc591\ud638\uc2e4)'''\n*The Infirmary teacher's name is Ge Bo-lin. Jong-min found a note in Ge Bo-lin's gown and the note says \"Sir, the password to the base is on the whiteboard, please erase it once memorize for security reason\". Members found the clue (4-4-6-9) by erasing the whiteboard.\n*Ho-dong forcefully opened a metal cabinet, hoping to find a clue like what he did in episode 1 but found nothing.\n*Shin-dong picked the lock of a miniature cabinet and receive a clue and paper. The paper is about the 2 bottles of empty \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" on the table of Consultation Room. The clue is the antidote for the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\".\n*When exiting the room, members witness four people in dark robes exiting from the upper floor and walked towards the other end of the corridor.\n'''4. Library (\ub3c4\uc11c\uad00)'''\n*In the book loan records, members observed that Mi-ra and Ho-li have loaned out a book call \"Sa-ra's key\".\n*Dong-hyun for a book that presumed to be the key to open the miniature cabinet. Since they have opened the miniature cabinet, the key was not longer available.\n*Shin-dong observed one of the bookshelves is odd and asked to Jong-min investigate. Jong-min found out one of the bookshelves can be lifted and found a door. The used the password (4-4-6-9) to open the door.\n'''5. Secret Den (\ube44\ubc00 \uc544\uc9c0\ud2b8)'''\n*Members found a video clip on the computer filming about a sacrificial ritual in progress. Byung-jae and P.O went back to the Consultant Room tho retrieve the test paper with all correct answer and return to Secret Den to continue with the discussion.\n*Behind the posters of male idol groups, members found a clue linking to the History teacher.\n**History teacher (Ge Su-sang) is actually a chief priest. Infirmary teacher (Ge Bo-lin) is the daughter of Ge Su-sang but is not on Ge Su-sang side.\n**Ge Bo-lin has filmed the sacrificial ritual to exposed hers father's misdeed.\n**The sacrificial ritual requires 11 young girls' soul for the Sun god to revive. 9 girls (including Sa-ra) were listed as the missing people for the past 4 years.\n**All the teachers are very respectful to chief priest Ge Su-sang.\n**All sacrificial being will be mummified.\n**Members also found the map of the second floor. Temple (\uc2e0\uc804), Preparation Room (\uc81c\uc0ac \uc900\ube44\uc2e4), Follower Dormitory (\uc2e0\ub3c4 \uc0dd\ud65c\uad00) and Rooftop.\n*Byung-jae found more clues from the computer. The members practice on how to recite the sacrificial phrase so that they might be able to join the ritual secretly.\n*Members again witness four people in dark robe carrying a stretcher with a Mi-ra laying on it. The fifth person in dark robe is presumably the Infirmary teacher (Ge Bo-lin) that dropped a bunch of keys on the floor.}}\n|rowspan=2|Yoo Byung-Jae\n|rowspan=2|\n|-\n!'''12'''\n|{{date|16 Sep 2018}}\n|style=text-align:left|{{hidden||\n'''6. 1st Floor Corridor (1\uce35 \ubcf5\ub3c4)'''\n*Members use the long poles and ropes from the Consultation Room and Secret Den to improvise as a \"hook\" to retrieve the keys and unlock the gate of the corridor that was locked by history teacher (Ge Su-sang) earlier.\n'''6.1 Store (\ub9e4\uc810)'''\n*After unlocking the gate, members rushed to the Store as they were famished.\n*Ho-dong's plan is to get the members to find the dark robes to disguise as the followers to save Mi-ra.\n'''7. Changing Room (\ud0c8\uc758\uc2e4)'''\n*Byung-Jae and P.O searched the Changing Room to find the dark robes that are put aside for washing.\n*Remaining members joined in to search the room. Dong-hyun accidentally found a push button when playing with the pile of sand in a container which reveal a secret room behind the mirror.\n'''8. Sacrificial Waiting Room (\ud76c\uc0dd\uc591 \ub300\uae30\uc2e4)'''\n*The room has Kim Mi-ra's coat on one of the table. Members also found Gu Ha-li laying unconsciously on the table. Byung-Jae sprayed the antidote that was recovered from the Infirmary Room to revive Ha-li from the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\".\n*Members asked Ha-li if she can recollect what happened to her and Mi-ra. Ha-li reply was she drank the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" given by the history teacher and became unconscious and Mi-ra also did the same thing. Ha-li presumes that Mi-ra was the first to be sacrificed.\n*Ha-li has some knowledge on how the followers will patrol the 2nd floor and members need to be stealthy. Ha-li reveals that the dark robe are available in the 2nd floor Follower Dormitory and Mi-ra should be in the 2nd floor Preparation Room. Members need to hurry to rescue Mi-ra before she is sacrificed.\n*Ho-dong's plan is to quickly go to the 2nd floor Follower Dormitory to put on the dark robe to disguise as the followers and go to the Preparation Room to rescue Mi-ra.\n*Ha-li suggested to first locate the whereabouts of Mi-ra.\n*At the 1st Floor Corridor, Byung-Jae mentioned that the members do not have the key to open the gate to the 2nd floor. Ha-li mentioned that the key should be in one of the books of the Library and Byung-Jae explained to Ha-li that there is no key in the book. Mi-ra was the last person to have borrowed the book. Members suddenly remembered that Mi-ra's coat was left in the Sacrificial Waiting Room, found the key and unlock gate to the 2nd floor.\n'''9. Preparation Room (\uc81c\uc0ac \uc900\ube44\uc2e4)'''\n*Members and Ha-li entered the room and found the partially mummified Mi-ra.\n*As Jong-min tried to retrieve the antidote to revive Mi-ra, the Infirmary teacher (Ge Bo-lin) appeared. She was shocked and told the members and Ha-li to hide as the followers are approaching.\n*The followers and Infirmary teacher left with the partially mummified Mi-ra to the Temple. Ho-dong was sad that they should have bring the antidote along and save Mi-ra.\n*Byung-Jae found Ha-li's photograph in the sarcophagus. Ha-li is supposed to be the 11th girl to be sacrificed.\n*P.O secretly return to the Sacrificial Waiting Room to retrieve the antidote.\n*With Mi-ra being brought to the Temple to be sacrificed, Ho-dong hurried the members to quickly retrieve the dark robes.\n''' 10. Follower Dormitory (\uc2e0\ub3c4 \uc0dd\ud65c\uad00)'''\n*Jong-min and Dong-hyun secretly entered the room to retrieve some dark robes as they also discovered that there are some followers in the room watching the television show.\n*Jong-min was excited to find 7 dark robes at one corner of the room. The remaining members also secretly entered the room.\n**Jong-min managed to be the first to put on the robe and scared the remaining members and Ha-li out of their wits to the Preparation Room as they thought they were being discovered.\n**In the Preparation Room, the members discussed that everyone was to go back to the Sacrificial Waiting Room. Jong-min re-enter the Follower Dormitory to retrieve the remaining 6 sets dark robes and return to the Sacrificial Waiting Room.\n**In the Sacrificial Waiting Room, members and Ha-li put on the dark robes.\n**Ho-dong entered the Store and found out the use of the remaining bunch of keys. One of the keys opened the door of the faulty vending machine to the Secret Laboratory.\n'''11. Secret Laboratory (\ube44\ubc00 \uc5f0\uad6c\uc2e4)'''\n*The Secret Laboratory is to manufacture the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\". Byung-jae remembered from the video that the followers will drink the \"Holy water\" during the ritual, the members can secretly put the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" to the \"Holy water\" and save Mi-ra once the followers have fallen unconscious.\n*Byung-jae found the recipe for making the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\", \"Holy water\" and courage pill (\uc6a9\uae30\ud658). The recipe book explained the usage of each potion. The anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic takes effect after 5 minutes to cause the users to be unconscious. After the followers have taken the anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic, members discussed that they should delay the ritual to let the anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic to take effect.\n*Members found out that the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\", \"Holy water\" and courage pill were already made in advance and left one the table.\n*Dong-hyun and Shin-dong each ate a courage pill.\n**Members and Ha-li returned to the Follower Dormitory to find a route to the Temple as the main door to the Temple is locked. They were unable to find any alternate route. They end up going back to the Preparation Room after learning that the ritual will start ten minutes.\n**Members and Ha-li go to the Secret Den to review the ritual video. Members discussed ways to mix the \"Holy water\" and \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" during the ritual.\n'''12. Temple (\uc2e0\uc804)'''\n*Members and Ha-li joined the sacrificial ritual. Byung-jae accidentally fell to the ground to create a distraction while Shin-dong and Jong-min will take care of Byuang-jae. Ho-dong and Dong-hyun will block the view of P.O pouring the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" into the pool of \"Holy water\".\n*Members created many distractions and delays to let the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" to take effect. Once the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" took effect, those who drank the \"anti-drowsiness nourishment tonic\" started to faint.\n*Members use the antidote to revive Mi-ra and Infirmary teacher (Ge Bo-lin). Ge Bo-lin was unable to escape with the members, Mi-ra and Ha-li due to his father (history teacher).\n*Members decode the password using the answer from the world history test which open a door.\n'''13. Secret Den (\ubc00\uc2e4)'''\n*In the room, there is a window that is pad-locked. Shin-dong and Dong-hyun were selected to retrieve the key from a hole of the false wall with worms and centipedes since they have taken the courage pill. Dong-Hyun finally retrieve the key after several attempts.\n*After unlocking the window, members and the 2 schoolgirls discovered that there is no way to go downward instead must go to the rooftop.\n'''14. Rooftop (\uc625\uc0c1)'''\n*Shin-dong leaped from the rooftop to the inflated balloon and open the front door of the school to left the remaining members and 2 schoolgirls out.\n*'''{{big|Escape successfully!!!}}''' (with the story character)}}\n|-\n!'''13'''\n|Special Episode\n|{{date|23 Sep 2018}}\n|colspan=3|Recap and behind the scene of the past 6 escapes.\n|End of Season 1\n|-\n|}\n{{hidden end}}\n\n===Season 2===\n{{hidden begin\n|title=List of Episodes (Season 2)\n|titlestyle=background:lightGray\n}}\n{|class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n! Episode #!! Challenge #!! style=width:15%|Original Airdate!! Scene!! Content/Area Explored!! Notes\n|-\n!rowspan=2|1\n|{{NA}}\n|rowspan=2|17 March 2019\n|Team meal meeting\n|style=text-align:left|{{HideH}}Members meet in advance and are briefed on the new challenge format\n|rowspan=3|\u2014\n|-\n|rowspan=2|1\n|rowspan=2|Mirae University<br>(\ubbf8\ub798\ub300\ud559\uad50)\n|style=text-align:left|{{HideH}}\n'''1. Gym (\uccb4\uc721\uad00)'''\n*'''Wooden Wardrobe'''\n**At the basketball court, there is a wooden cabinet with a note \"Never to open\" (\uc808\ub300\uc5f4\uc9c0\ub9c8\uc2dc\uc624) and Jong-min was selected to open the cabinet.\n**As he opened the cabinet, a cabinet full of tennis balls spills out.\n*'''Target practice board''' (mounted on the 2nd floor of the gym)\n**The cast used the tennis balls from the wooden cabinet to throw through the bulls-eye of target practice board.\n**P.O succeed in getting a tennis ball through the bulls-eye after a few tries.\n**2 banners are released to congratulate the cast on the first recording of Season 2 (\ub300\ud0c8\ucd9c2 \uccab\ub179\ud654 \uc218\uace0\ud558\uc138\uc694 \ud30c\uc774\ud305).\n'''2. Gym Corridor (\uccb4\uc721\uad00 \ubcf5\ub3c4)'''\n*The cast observed a long stick on the ground. They think it is the high jump pole. They decided to put it aside as it might be useful later.\n*There is a chained glass door at the end of the corridor. The writings of posters tell the cast that the Gym is off-limit to the students of Mirae University and only men in black suits and those in white gowns are allowed. The cast think it might be linked to UFOs or secret experiments.\n*The cast also search the metal lockers for hints. A document that was written in the year 2014 was found and the cast thinks that the locker has not been open since then.\n*'''Fire hose box'''\n**While the cast was searching the place for hints, Ho-dong stumbled upon the empty fire hose box which is suspicious.\n**P.O pressed the button on the fire hose box and the locked panel next to it opened. A secret flight of stairs is revealed.\n'''3. Basement 1 (\uc9c0\ud558 1\uce35)'''\n\n'''3.1 Conference Room (\ud68c\uc758\uc2e4)'''\n*The cast learn from the information on the white board that there a loud bang occurred and the staff in the University tried to keep a secret about the incident.\n*The cast learn about the secret of Black Tower and history of '''Secret Security Association''' (SSA) from the laptop.\n*Byung-jae found a security access card (with lanyard) on opening of the ventilation shaft.\n*Initially, the cast thought of jumping on the trampoline to retrieve. Ho-dong suddenly remembered about the long pole found on the Gym Corridor.\n*Ho-dong rushed back to the Gym Corridor to retrieve the long pole. The remaining cast laugh at Ho-dong as the flag-pole in the Conference Room is long enough to retrieve the access card.\n*The cast eventually use the long pole from the Gym Hallway to retrieve the access card.\n*The SSA Visitor access card has an access to B area.\n\n'''3.2 Branch Manager's room (\uc9c0\ubd80\uc7a5\uc2e4)'''\n*The cast used the SSA Visitor access card to open the door to the room.\n*The Branch manager's name is Oh Ji-gu (\uc624\uc9c0\uad6c).\n*The cast looked at Oh Ji-gu's email inbox for clues/hints. They opened an email titled \"RACCOON I\" and instructed to download a movie file. The movie file is password protected to be downloaded.\n*P.O & Byung-jae found a de-cryption security card behind the desk organiser.\n*Shin-dong decode using the codes on the de-cryption security card and filename of the movie file. He entered \"OJIGUMAN\" and the movie file started to download.\n*The movie file is a closed circuit TV recording of the mysterious gas causing the researchers and security guards to died.\n*After viewing the movie file, the cast look around the room for other clues. Byung-jae exited the room to the Basement 1 hallway and found the hallway with strange black cables from the Control Room (Upper). He return to the room to get the remaining cast to investigate.\n\nBasement 1 Hallway (\uc9c0\ud558 1\uce35 \ubcf5\ub3c4)\n*The cast found strange cables from the Control Room (Upper) to other rooms. They left the area as they are unable to figure out.\n\n'''3.3 Cafeteria (\uc2dd\ub2f9)'''\n*The cast return to the cafeteria and was figuring out on opening the glass door. Shin-dong suddenly remembered that there are magnets on the whiteboard in the Conference Room and retrieved it.\n*The cast spent some time to lift the bar using the magnets from the glass door. Shin-dong go to the Branch Manager's room to retrieve some papers, folded the papers and finally lift the crossbar.\n*There is protection vest hanging on the broken glass window and the cast found an SSA Visitor access card with access to C area and the light flare. The protection vest belongs to Guard Jo Geun-man.\n*The cast also saw a body at the basement 2 of the building. The cast suspected that the person must have jumped out of the window to escape the mysterious gas.\n*Shin-dong saw the EXIT sign on the basement 2 and guess they will be escaping through there.\n*The cast had a sumptuous meal at the cafeteria before continuing with the escape.\n\n'''3.4 Hangar (Upper) (\uaca9\ub0a9\uace0 ((\u4e0a))'''\n*The cast used the SSA Visitor access card with access to C area to open the door. The lighting in the room turned off after a short while and the light flare from the cafeteria comes in handy.\n*The cast observe there are huge amount of black cables from the hangar door.\n*P.O manage to find the lighting switch for the hangar and the cast are surprised on their discovery of the Black Tower (\uac80\uc740\ud0d1).\n|-\n!2\n|24 March 2019\n|style=text-align:left|{{HideH}}\n'''3.4a Hangar (Upper) (\uaca9\ub0a9\uace0 ((\u4e0a))'''\n*The cast found the dead researchers at the corner of the hangar. They decided to climb down the ladder to investigate.\n*As the cast approach the Black Tower (\uac80\uc740\ud0d1), a console with Red, Yellow and Blue buttons appear. After a while, a bar timer countdown and the white smoke start to spray out of the Black Tower. The cast escaped the hangar and enter the security room.\n\n'''3.5a Security Room (\ubcf4\uc548\uc2e4)'''\n*From the room, the cast see the Black Tower displaying special symbols on the screen via the CCTV.\n*The cast communicated with the AI robot in the room and manage to learn more about the Black Tower. The Black Tower is a UFO. AI robot warned the cast not to inhale the white smoke from the Black Tower as it has killed all the researchers.\n*The AI robot informed the cast that after the incident of the white smoke, RACCOON I has been activated. The AI Robot suggested to the cast to visit the Language Lab to learn about the strange symbols.\n*As the white smoke is deadly, the AI robot informs the cast that the gas protection vests and masks are located in the Storeroom next to the Security Room.\n*P.O discovered that there is a secret entrance to the storeroom beneath the desk of the room.\n\n'''3.6 Storeroom (\ucc3d\uace0)'''\n*P.O crawl through the secret entrance and found a dead researcher (\uc720\uc9c0\uc2dd). P.O found the access card for Area D.\n*Byung-jae crawl through the secret entrance to help P.O to find the gas protection vests and masks.\n\n'''3.5b Security Room (\ubcf4\uc548\uc2e4)'''\n*Back in the Security Room, AI robot informs that to access the Language Lab, they will need an access card for Area E. Staff with access card for Area E are usually in the Control Room.\n*The cast put on the gas protection vests and masks so that they can avoid inhaling and in contact with the white smoke.\n*Jong-min, P.O, Shin-dong and Dong-hyun stayed behind in the room to observe.\n\n'''3.4